// Paragraph 1: The Search, Rescue, and Revival
line_1 = "After a grueling search through the collapsing, pitch-black depths, I finally found him...\n\nHe was trapped in the core chamber, fused to the life-support of the Blackstone Goliath. It was a desperate fight, but by overloading the steam valves, we shattered the beast's grip and pulled him free from its biological clutch. I managed to revive him just in time.";

// Paragraph 2: The Return to the Light
line_2 = "Exhausted, battered, but walking side-by-side once again, we crawled out of the mountain's shadow just as the morning sun broke over Greyford.\n\nWe survived the Blackstone. We brought each other back. And some secrets are better left buried in the dark.\n\n\n[ PRESS SPACE TO END GAME ]";

